sourcesContent:
export const gymEquipmentGuides = {
  "leg-press": {
    name: "Leg Press Machine",
    description: "A machine that allows you to press weight away from your body using your legs while in a seated position.",
    videoId: "IZxyjW7MPJQ",
    instructions: [
      "Sit in the machine with your back against the pad",
      "Place feet shoulder-width apart on the platform",
      "Lower the weight slowly until knees are at 90 degrees",
      "Push through your heels to return to starting position"
    ],
    recommendations: {
      beginnerReps: "10-12 reps",
      beginnerSets: "3 sets",
      intermediateReps: "12-15 reps",
      intermediateSets: "4 sets",
      advancedReps: "15-20 reps",
      advancedSets: "4-5 sets",
      restTime: "90-120 seconds between sets"
    }
  },
  "chest-press": {
    name: "Chest Press Machine",
    description: "A machine that simulates a bench press movement in a more controlled manner.",
    videoId: "xUm0BiZCWlQ",
    instructions: [
      "Adjust seat height so handles are at chest level",
      "Grip handles with palms facing forward",
      "Push handles forward until arms are extended",
      "Slowly return to starting position"
    ],
    recommendations: {
      beginnerReps: "8-10 reps",
      beginnerSets: "3 sets",
      intermediateReps: "10-12 reps",
      intermediateSets: "3-4 sets",
      advancedReps: "12-15 reps",
      advancedSets: "4 sets",
      restTime: "60-90 seconds between sets"
    }
  },
  "lat-pulldown": {
    name: "Lat Pulldown Machine",
    description: "A cable machine with a long bar attachment used to work the latissimus dorsi muscles.",
    videoId: "CAwf7n6Luuc",
    instructions: [
      "Sit with thighs secured under the pad",
      "Grip the bar wider than shoulder width",
      "Pull the bar down to upper chest level",
      "Control the bar as you return to start"
    ],
    recommendations: {
      beginnerReps: "10-12 reps",
      beginnerSets: "3 sets",
      intermediateReps: "12-15 reps",
      intermediateSets: "3-4 sets",
      advancedReps: "15-20 reps",
      advancedSets: "4 sets",
      restTime: "60-90 seconds between sets"
    }
  },
  "seated-row": {
    name: "Seated Row Machine",
    description: "A machine that works your back muscles through a rowing motion.",
    videoId: "GZbfZ033f74",
    instructions: [
      "Sit with chest against the pad",
      "Grab handles with arms extended",
      "Pull handles to your chest",
      "Slowly return to starting position"
    ],
    recommendations: {
      beginnerReps: "10-12 reps",
      beginnerSets: "3 sets",
      intermediateReps: "12-15 reps",
      intermediateSets: "4 sets",
      advancedReps: "15-20 reps",
      advancedSets: "4-5 sets",
      restTime: "60-90 seconds between sets"
    }
  },
  "shoulder-press": {
    name: "Shoulder Press Machine",
    description: "A machine designed for overhead pressing movements to target shoulder muscles.",
    videoId: "Wqq43dKW1TU",
    instructions: [
      "Adjust seat so handles are at shoulder height",
      "Grip handles with palms facing forward",
      "Press handles overhead until arms extend",
      "Lower slowly back to shoulder level"
    ],
    recommendations: {
      beginnerReps: "8-10 reps",
      beginnerSets: "3 sets",
      intermediateReps: "10-12 reps",
      intermediateSets: "3-4 sets",
      advancedReps: "12-15 reps",
      advancedSets: "4 sets",
      restTime: "60-90 seconds between sets"
    }
  },
  "leg-extension": {
    name: "Leg Extension Machine",
    description: "A machine that targets the quadriceps through knee extension.",
    videoId: "YyvSfVjQeL0",
    instructions: [
      "Sit with back against pad",
      "Hook feet under ankle pad",
      "Extend legs until straight",
      "Lower slowly back to starting position"
    ],
    recommendations: {
      beginnerReps: "12-15 reps",
      beginnerSets: "3 sets",
      intermediateReps: "15-20 reps",
      intermediateSets: "3-4 sets",
      advancedReps: "20-25 reps",
      advancedSets: "4 sets",
      restTime: "45-60 seconds between sets"
    }
  },
  "leg-curl": {
    name: "Leg Curl Machine",
    description: "A machine that targets the hamstrings through knee flexion.",
    videoId: "1Tq3QdYUuHs",
    instructions: [
      "Lie face down on machine",
      "Hook ankles under pad",
      "Curl legs up towards buttocks",
      "Lower slowly back to start"
    ],
    recommendations: {
      beginnerReps: "12-15 reps",
      beginnerSets: "3 sets",
      intermediateReps: "15-20 reps",
      intermediateSets: "3-4 sets",
      advancedReps: "20-25 reps",
      advancedSets: "4 sets",
      restTime: "45-60 seconds between sets"
    }
  },
  "cable-machine": {
    name: "Cable Machine",
    description: "A versatile machine with adjustable cables for various exercises.",
    videoId: "WzVMjf1m_jk",
    instructions: [
      "Adjust cable height as needed",
      "Select appropriate attachment",
      "Maintain proper form throughout",
      "Control weight in both directions"
    ],
    recommendations: {
      beginnerReps: "10-12 reps",
      beginnerSets: "3 sets",
      intermediateReps: "12-15 reps",
      intermediateSets: "3-4 sets",
      advancedReps: "15-20 reps",
      advancedSets: "4 sets",
      restTime: "60-90 seconds between sets"
    }
  }
};
